msgid "Server transfer copies ONLY AI/STT providers, URLs, models and keys — local UI, profiles, devices and snippets stay unchanged. Use it to carry your server setup to another PC. Export writes those server fields (INCLUDING keys) to a .json; import shows a preview and asks you to confirm before applying."
